'''''5P8''''' was a [[Prowler-class reconnaissance vessel|''Prowler''-class reconnaissance vessel]] of the [[New Republic Defense Fleet/Legends|New Republic Defense Fleet]].

Attached to the [[New Republic Fifth Fleet|New Republic Fifth Battle Group]] during the [[Black Fleet Crisis]], ''5P8'' discovered the drifting [[TIE/IN interceptor/Legends|TIE/IN interceptor]] of [[Plat Mallar]] while scanning the space surrounding the [[Koornacht Cluster/Legends|Koornacht Cluster]].

